 "remarks": "Nestled on two acres in one of New Canaan&apos;s established residential neighborhoods, this classic Colonial offers timeless appeal and exceptional potential. Built in 1983, the home offers a solid foundation and been recently painted throughout the interior, creating a fresh, light-filled atmosphere ready for its next owners. The bright and inviting kitchen serves as the heart of the home, while generous living spaces provide comfort for everyday living and entertaining alike. An expansive unfinished basement offers an outstanding opportunity to create additional living space, whether a recreation room, home gym, office, or media room. Conveniently located close to New Canaan&apos;s vibrant village, parks, shopping, dining, and commuter options, this property presents an opportunity to enjoy the best of New Canaan living while adding your own personal touches.",
